*''Policy and Opinion in the Gulf War'', University of Chicago Press 1994, ISBN 0-226-54565-2
*''Retreat from Doomsday: The Obsolescence of Major War'', Basic Books 1989, ISBN 0-465-06939-8 [http://psweb.sbs.ohio-state.edu/faculty/jmueller/doom.pdf]
